Bandung, Indonesia\r\n	1983	:	Bab-Bab tentang Hypotheek published by PT Alumni,\r\n			Bandung, Indonesia\r\n	1979	:	Bab-Bab tentang Credietverband, Gadai & Fiducia, \r\n			published by PT Alumni, Bandung, Indonesia\r\n	1978	:	Perjanjian Kredit Bank published by PT Alumni, Bandung, \r\n			Indonesia\r\n\r\n14.	RESEARCH\r\n	1994	:	Comparative Research on the System of Registration for \r\n			Security of Moveable Goods in Singapore, Hong Kong, and \r\n			Japan, Sponsored by ELIPS, USAID\r\n	1990	:	Comparative Research on Coffee Arbitration in the State \r\n				of New York, USA, Rotterdam, the Netherlands and Norway, \r\n				Sponsored by the Association of Indonesian Coffee Exporters \r\n				(AICE)\r\n\r\n15.	SPEAKER AT VARIOUS SEMINARS\r\n	&#61553;	2011:	&#61550;   “Good Corporate Governance” Seminar, Conducted by  Finance and Development Supervisory Agency BPKP, Jakarta\r\n	&#61553;	2007:	&#61550;	“Technical Assistance on Contract Drafting” Seminar, Conducted Through the Co-operation of the Ministry of Finance and State Administrative Board\r\n				“Women Empowerment” Seminar, Conducted by Juanda University, Bogor, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	2006:	&#61550;	“Corruptions and Policy” Seminar, Sponsored by the ”Golongan Karya” Political Party, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	2004:	&#61550;	Credit Syndication and Restructurization” Seminar for Judges, Sponsored by Center for Legal Research and the Supreme Court, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	”Boundaries of Unlawful Conducts in Civil and Criminal Laws” Seminar, Sponsored by Judiciary Attorney, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	2003: 	&#61550;	”National Law Development VII” Seminar, Sponsored by the National Law Development Center of the Ministry of Justice of Indonesia, Bali, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	Seminar on the Subject of UNCITRAL, Conducted by the Central Bank of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	2002:	&#61550;	Seminar on the Subject of Geographical Indicator at the Embassy of France, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	2001:	&#61550;	“Cyber Law” Seminar, Conducted by the Surabaya Effects Exchange (BES), Surabaya, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Cyber Law” Seminar, Conducted by Yayasan Pendidikan Graha Kirana, Medan, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1998:	&#61550;	“Utilization of Vacant Land” Seminar, Sponsored by the Ministry of Agraria of Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Monetary Crisis, Force Majeure, Changes of Circumstances and Good Faith in the Civil Law System” Seminar, Conducted by Law Offices of  Remy & Darus, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1997:	&#61550;	“Contract Law in the Era of Globalization” seminar, conducted by the National Law Development Center of the Ministry of Justice, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1996:	&#61550;	“System of Law Concerning Security Rights on Property (“Hak Tanggungan”)” Seminar, Conducted by the Faculty of Law, University of Padjadjaran, Bandung, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Security Rights on Property” Seminar, Conducted by University of North Sumatra, Medan, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1995:	&#61550;	“Housing and Residential Law” Seminar, Conducted by the State Minister for National Housing, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1994:	&#61550;	“Doing Business by State-Owned Company (Perum) for Pledge, Conducted by the University of Brawijaya, Malang, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Legal and Practical Implication of Strata Title” Seminar, Conducted by Business Focus, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	Seminar on the Subject of Banking Liquidation, Conducted the Central Bank of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1993:	&#61550;	“Basic Principles of Credit Agreement Law in Indonesia” Seminar, Conducted by the Central Bank of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Basic Concept of Contract Law”, Conducted by ELIPS, USAID, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Freedom of Contract and Its Relationship with Standard Form Contracts” Seminar, Conducted by the Indonesian Association of Public Notaries, Surabaya, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Basic Framework of Security Laws in Indonesia” Seminar, Conducted by ELIPS, USAID, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Liquidation of Banking Companies Pursuant to the Banking Law” Seminar, Conducted by the Indonesian Central Bank, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n			&#61550;	“Credit Recovery” Seminar, Conducted by the Indonesian Association of Public Notaries, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1992:	&#61550;	“Rights on Security Over Land” Seminar, Conducted by the National Law Development Center of the Ministry of Justice of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1989:	&#61550;	“Land Policy and Management in Urban Areas and Its Implementation” Workshop, Conducted by the Ministry of Public Works, Bali, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1988:	&#61550;	“Hire Purchase Agreement” Seminar, Conducted by the National Law Development Center of the Ministry of Justice of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1986:	&#61550;	“The Implementation of State Philosophy Pancasila in National Civil Law”, Conducted by the National Law Development Center of the Ministry of Justice of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1984:	&#61550;	“Legal Issues of State-Owned Companies”, Conducted by the National Law Development Center of the Ministry of Justice of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1983:	&#61550;	“Settlement of Commercial Disputes, Conducted by General Assembly of ASEAN Lawyers Association, Manila, the Philippines\r\n	&#61553;	1980:	&#61550;	“Consumer Protection in Standard Form Contracts”, Conducted by the National Law Development Center of the Ministry of Justice of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1978:	&#61550;	“Right to Build on Leased Land”, Conducted by the National Law Development Center of the Ministry of Justice of Indonesia, Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n16.	MEMBERSHIPS\r\na.	Professional Memberships\r\n	&#61553;	2005 – Present	:	&#61550;	Member of Arbitrators of Indonesian National  \r\n									Board of Arbitration (BANI), Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n								&#61550;	Chairman of BANI Branch of Medan, Medan,\r\n									Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1999 - Present	:	&#61550;	Member of the Indonesian Association of Fishermen \r\n									(HNSI), Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n	&#61553;	1988 - Present	:	&#61550;	Chairman of Legal and Arbitration Department of \r\n									the Association of Indonesian Coffee Exporters \r\n									(AICE), Jakarta, Indonesia\r\n\r\nb.	Other Memberships\r\n&#61553;	Forum for Corporate the Government Indonesia (FCGI) (2003 - Present)\r\n&#61553;	Netherlands Alumni Association\r\n&#61553;	Indonesian Lawyers Association\r\n&#61553;	Indonesian Women Lawyers Association\r\n&#61553;	ASEAN Lawyers Association\r\n&#61553;	The Alumni of South Western Lawyers, Dallas, Texas, USA\r\n&#61553;	Indonesian Islamic Intellectual Society (ICMI)\r\n&#61553;	Association of Indonesian Coffee Exporters (AICE)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n17.	AWARD AND ACHIEVEMENT \r\n&#61553;	Satya Lancana Karya Awarded by President of Republic Indonesia in 1989\r\n&#61553;	Bintang Satya Lancana Dwidya Sistha Awarded by President of Republic Indonesia in 2012\r\n&#61553;	Assigned as Member of Langkat Sultanate Royal Family with Datuk Cendekia Negri title given with full authority by Royal Langkat Sultanate Ceremony in March 2013 \r\n\r\n* * * * * *\r\n', '-'),
