(30, 'The Commercial Laws of Indonesia', 2, '15;', 'I/1998', '979-414-785-0', '1998-09-07', 316, 44200, 'Buku ini membahas tentang Hukum Dagang Indonesia dengan penekanan pada topik tentang pokok-pokok permasalahan hukum dagang internasional, dengan materi pembahasan yang cukup luas, yang di antaranya adalah mengenai prosedur hukum perdata internasional, pengakuan dan pelaksanaan putusan pengadilan asing dan putusan badan arbitrase. Dibahas pula mengenai penanaman modal asing, hukum perseroan, permasalahan hukum dalam hubungan bisnis oleh orang asing di Indonesia dan juga tentang perpajakan yang berhubungan dengan hukum dagang.', 'nPREFACE<br>CONTENTS<br>INTRODUCTION TO INDONESIAN CIVIL<br>AND COMMERCIAL LAW<br>Diversity of Civil and Commercial Law<br>-Legal Pluralism<br>-Government Regulation 1945 No.2<br>-Basis for Legal Pluralism<br>-The Private Law for The European Group<br>-The Codes:Civil and Commercial Code<br>-Supreme Court Circular Letter 1963<br>-The New Order Approach<br>The Judicial System<br>-General Courts<br>-Religious Courts<br>-Military Courts<br>-Administrative Courts<br>INTERNATIONAL CIVIL PROCEDURE<br>Jurisdiction<br>-The Basis of Jurisdiction<br>*Forum rei<br>*Forum actoris<br>-Jurisdiction to Enjoint and to Arrest<br>-Jurisdiction in REM<br>Constraints<br>-Forum Non Conveniens<br>Forum Selection<br>-Choice of Forum and Choice of Law in Indonesian Practice<br>-Examples of Case Law<br>Lis Alibi Pendens<br>Imunities<br>Service of Process<br>Taking of Evidence Abroad<br>RECOGNITION AND ENFORCEMENT OF FOREIGN JUDGMENTS<br>Foreign Judments As a Rule Not Enforceable in Indonesia<br>-Text of Article 436 RV<br>-Principle Of Territorial Sovereignty<br>*No execution treties between indonesia and other states<br>*General average decisions as exception<br>*Condemnatory or declaratory jugments<br>*Declaratory decisions<br>*Advice of counsel to foreign clients<br>Summary<br>ARBITRATION<br>Arbitration<br>-Law on Arbiration<br>-practice of Arbiration<br>-Hotel 